        <abstract>
            <p>Describes meeting of Geological Society [1 June 1853].</p>
            <p>Mentions his criticism of Murchison’s lecture on flints.</p> 
<p>Describes Robert Chambers’ "On the glacial phenomena in Scotland" [<hi rend="italic">Edinburgh New Philos. J.</hi> 54 (1853): 229–82].</p> 
            <p>Mentions controversial election of members to the Royal Society.</p>
        </abstract>
